stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft : Contract scaffolded
    Draft --> Configured : Governance approval<br/>+ parameters set
    Configured --> ActiveContributions : First contribution window opens
    ActiveContributions --> GracePeriod : Deadline reached
    GracePeriod --> ActiveContributions : Late member submitted
    GracePeriod --> ReadyForPayout : All dues settled
    ActiveContributions --> ReadyForPayout : All members paid in early

    ReadyForPayout --> PayoutInProgress : Treasury executes payout instruction
    PayoutInProgress --> ActiveContributions : Next rotation begins
    PayoutInProgress --> CycleComplete : Final recipient paid

    CycleComplete --> Archived : Metadata snapshot + audit hash stored
    Archived --> [*]

    %% Exceptional paths
    Configured --> Paused : Emergency halt (governance)
    ActiveContributions --> Paused : Risk mitigation
    Paused --> Configured : Governance resume signal

